title: Simon R. Green-From Hell With Love  A Secret Histories Novel
description:
From Hell With Love  A Secret Histories Novel
by Simon R. Green

   
New York Times best-selling author Simon R. Green creates a fantastical world in his Secret Histories series, in which the Drood family protects mankind from creatures of the night. Eddie Drood is not happy about being the new head of the family, especially now that everyone believes either he or his girlfriend Molly was responsible for the former matriarch's death. Since Eddie knows he didn't do it, he doesn't like where this is going
